    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《Zaxoid》中面对外星入侵，这是一款令人肾上腺素飙升的roguelite双摇杆太空射击游戏！通过升级你的飞船或强化你的城市来防御银河系免受无情入侵者的攻击，战略选择让每次游戏都独一无二。使用双摇杆进行精准的混乱战斗，转换为坦克模式以击退地面入侵，保护你的居民。激烈的游戏体验带你回到游戏的黄金时代。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2124050/extras/1da5a13d62709dbfdc9f1efff1381c73.avif?t=1771783254\" width=565 height=225 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>拿起你的游戏手柄，体验激烈、精准的战斗和真正的街机氛围</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2124050/extras/617fa6f6dca7df6cef0fe05d6b2e0160.avif?t=1771783254\" width=565 height=178 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>为你的飞船和城市获取史诗级升级，每次游戏打造独特的配置</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2124050/extras/f838c8149051a02db84612971d8c7413.avif?t=1771783254\" width=565 height=195 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>建造炮塔、克隆设施和太空计划来保护你的居民</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2124050/extras/60b715494174244ddc84b6baecd97358.avif?t=1771783254\" width=565 height=195 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>切换到坦克模式，粉碎地面入侵，应对来自太空和地面的威胁</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
